Generic Targets:
   noargs|all|help|targets Print this text and exit
   usage                   Print more detailed information on each target
Global Building Targets:
   all_all                 Build all packages (works best on Linux)
   depend_all              Perform `make depend' for all packages
   forcedepend_all         Perform `make forcedepend' for all packages
Global Maintenance Targets:
   clean_all               Perform `make clean' for all packags
   distclean_all           Perform `make distclean' for all packages
   pull_all                Perform `make pull' for all packages
   commit_all              Perform `make commit' for all packages
Git Maintenance Targets:
   pull                    An alias to `git pull'
   tag_all                 Perform `make tag' for all packages
   forcetag_all            Perform `make forcetag' for all packages
Git Addition Targets:
   import                  Import current working directory to git
   commit                  An alias to `git commit'
